data.description: Welcome to this inviting 3,700SF home perched above the 10th hole of North Shore GC. This 4 bdrm home features an open main living w/gorgeous hardwoods, frml dining & office spc. Kitchen w/large island, SS appliances including double oven & flows seamlessly into your family rm w/an elegant fireplace. Main lvl primary w/ensuite offering a soaking tub, vanity w/dual sinks & walk-in closet. Lower lvl boasts a huge rec rm, media rm w/wet bar, dual sided FP, addtnl bdrms, bath & opens to the outdoor spc. Spacious 3-car garage & large crawl w/potential to turn into an addtnl living area. New roof, ext paint & deck stain. Exceptional location near beautiful parks, Norpoint community center, great schools & all amenities this amazing area has offer
